<title>tsbyḥ bṣwty̱ yʿlạlk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - tsbyḥ bṣwty̱ yʿlạlk whtạf lạ̹smk ạlbhy̱ tmjyd lsẖkẖṣk wjlạlk rwḥk yswd yạạ̹lhy̱ (2) 1- yạrb ạftḥ ynbwʿ kẖyrk lạ tmnʿ ạlbrkẗ ʿny̱ hạ̉ndẖạ ạḥml nyrk w lmjdk ạnạ mstny̱ (2) 2- yqwlwạ nạjḥ mạnạ ạbnk lạ̉nk dạymạaⁿ btʿny̱ w mdạm mʿạk w bḥbk mạ sẖy̱ʾ fy̱ ạldnyạ yfsẖlny̱ (2) 3- rby̱ ḥyạty̱ mn gẖyrk mạtsạwysẖ w lạ tjny̱ ạ̉y̱ tẖmr lmjdk byk qwty̱ wlyk ạ̉gẖny̱ (2) 4- yạyswʿ hyn ḥmlk tʿạl bqwẗ w ạrfʿny̱ mḥtạj ạ̉nạ lmsẗ ydk dy̱ ṣlạty̱ lyk ạ̹smʿny̱ (2)</lyrics>
</song>